<pb facs="1361366" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> Viro
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></opener>
<p>
<lb/>Diu reditum tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in istam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Urbem</rs> expectavimus
         <lb/>Vir Amicissime. Te autem optima cum valetu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dine istic<del>e</del> pervenisse maxime gratulor. Tibi
         <lb/>gratias plurimas refero qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>d me de tuo reditu
         <lb/>sine cunctatione certiorem feceris, simulque
         <lb/><abbr>eruditiss.<hi rend="sup">as</hi></abbr> Incomparabilis <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> Tui <rs key="B_1717-10-17_991170515153305501" type="letter">litteras</rs>
<lb/>a me summo cum gaudio acceptas atque perlec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tas, transmiseris. In his enim <add>s<unclear>ci</unclear>tu</add><!-- ToDo: mit Fritz besprechen, um welches Wort es sich hier handeln könnte. --> pulcherrima,
         <lb/><del>ad </del>atque ad rem, in qua nunc strenue versor,
         <lb/>pertinentia invenio. Quo ad me attinet
         <lb/>scias velim me Tibi quam maxime esse
         <lb/><choice><sic>devictum</sic><corr>devinctum</corr></choice> et perpetuo ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>vinculo adstrictum. Antequam domum
         <lb/>redirem<add> heri</add> <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Noster Procurator
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupolus</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me sciscitatus fuit annon
         <lb/>Tu brevi adventurus esses, cui respondi
         <lb/>me sperare Te iam esse <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs>.
         <lb/>Et profecto spes mea haudquaquam me fefellit.
         <lb/>Rem gratam feceris ipsi <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupolo</rs>
         <lb/>nec non <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">is</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1253768439" type="person">Venerio</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089586175" type="person">Superantio</rs>
<pb facs="1361367" n="2"/>
<lb/>ac ipsi Secretario <rs key="pers_DE-588-1222289342" type="person">G<unclear>a</unclear>ldaldino</rs>, <add>si</add> reditum tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>ad inserviend<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Suis Excellentiis, <add>iisdem</add> significa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>veris, et quidem quam primum fieri poterit.
         <lb/><rs type="person">Frater</rs><!-- persontag --> <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178493288" type="person">Mari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Labia</rs> gaudet
         <lb/>de tuo reditu Tibique salutem plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
         <lb/>mittit. <rs key="pers_DE-588-100704514" type="person">Wetstenii</rs> <rs key="biblio_RC6TN74M" type="biblio">Flores Eloquenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> per
         <lb/>Tabellari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> meis expensis ut mittas rogo
         <lb/>mihique eodem tempore significes pre<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> eiusdem <rs key="biblio_RC6TN74M" type="biblio">libelli</rs> ut d<subst><del><gap/></del><add>e</add></subst>bito meo satis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>facere valeam. Quum <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs> petes,
         <lb/>ut me tribus aut duobus ante discessum diebus
         <lb/>certiorem facias rogo, domumque meam
         <lb/>sine ullis ceremoniis venias, in qua para<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum pro te cubile, et lectum servo.
         <lb/><choice><orig>non</orig><reg>Non</reg></choice> enim volo ut posthac sumptus super<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fluos in hac <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Civitate</rs> pro hospitio aut pro
         <lb/>cibariis efficias. <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">Litteras</rs><!-- brieftag Brief Nic II - Michelotti--> tandem <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr>
<lb/>consanguinei Tui <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicolai</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> datas
         <lb/>ante quindecim dies acc<unclear>e</unclear>pi magna cum
         <lb/>L<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>titia, ipsique illico <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">respondi</rs> rogans
         <lb/>simul ut saltem post un<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aut alte<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>r<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> annum redeat huc in domum
         <pb facs="1361369" n="3"/>
<lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>, permaneatque donec tandem aliquan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>do fiat istic Tui Successor.</p><closer>Vale Vir <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr>
<lb/>meque ad Tua mandata <abbr>paratiss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> crede.
            <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a.d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1717-11-01">1 Novembris 1717</date></dateline></closer>
